ks out, so there don't appear to be any critical issues here. The column names in s4's tables—グループID, ユーザID, ユーザIDロック, 有効日(From), 有効日(To), 認可単位ID, リクエストID—are missing from the hints, even though they'd be valuable for someone searching about table schema configuration. The hints do mention higher-level concepts like システムアカウント and 認可単位, but not these specific property names that users would likely look for.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23393,"cache_read_input_tokens":29873,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":23393,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"008fdb7c-dc3a-48b7-8b84-54b76c248b31","uuid":"a2795fb0-96af-450b-b91f-2bdb075d8a3b"}
